games.comment: Jeremy Maclin deep for a 51-yard touchdown. Maclin finished with 6 receptions for 142 yards and 2 scores.

Jeremy Maclin dropped a pass on the third down on the opening drive. However, the Ravens picked up the slack after that and roasted Detroit's incompetent defense. Flacco finished 23-of-36 for 269 yards and 2 touchdowns. He has struggled for most of the season, but this was 1 of his best performances. He hit some bombs, particularly to Wallace, and he didn't make many mistakes.    Wallace ended up leading the Ravens with 5 catches and 116 yards.
